    "faq_home_6nkgUA": {
      "type": "faq-home",
      "blocks": {
        "question_EdMtQg": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What tire brands does Prince Tires carry?",
            "answer": "<p>Prince Tires stocks a wide range of trusted tire brands to fit every budget. We carry premium names like Michelin, Bridgestone, Goodyear, Toyo, Cooper, Falken, and Continental, alongside high-quality affordable brands including Firemax, Linglong, Farroad, Yeada, and Fortune. Whether you need winter tires, all-season tires, or summer performance tires, we'll match you with the right brand for your vehicle and driving habits.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_MeiEVe": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long does a tire installation take?",
            "answer": "<p>A standard 4-tire installation takes about 30-45 minutes. We also handle TPMS sensor resets and wheel balancing as part of every install. Booking an appointment guarantees your time slot and lets us have your tires ready when you arrive.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_4WeWX3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do I need an appointment at Prince Tires?",
            "answer": "<p>We recommend booking an appointment to guarantee your tire service or purchase is completed during your visit. Appointments allow us to have the right tires ready and a bay reserved for your vehicle, so there's no waiting around. That said, walk-in customers are always welcome at Prince Tires, we'll do our best to help you on the spot, but we can't guarantee same-visit availability for tires or services without an appointment. To book ahead, call us at (403) 452-4283 or schedule online through our website.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_9xBRnL": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What tire services does Prince Tires offer?",
            "answer": "<p>We handle everything tire-related so you can get back on the road quickly. Our services include new tire sales and installation, tire balancing, tire rotation, flat tire repair, and TPMS (tire pressure monitoring system) service. Every installation is done by experienced technicians who've been fitting tires for Calgary's roads and weather conditions for over a decade.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_jDYb6X": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Why should I choose Prince Tires over other tire shops in Calgary?",
            "answer": "<p>Prince Tires has been one of Calgary's most recognized tire specialists for over 5 years. What started as a two-bay shop on Macleod Trail has grown into a go-to destination for drivers across the city. We combine a huge selection of tire brands at every price point with fast, professional installation and honest pricing. Our team focuses exclusively on tires, which means you're getting advice and service from true specialists.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_WMT7t6": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you sell wheels and rims?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! In addition to tires, Prince Tires carries a wide selection of wheels and rims from brands like XF Off-Road, Armed, RTX, ENVY, and RSSW. Whether you're looking for rugged off-road wheels or sleek street rims, we'll help you find the perfect style and fitment for your vehicle. Contact us at (403) 452-4283 or request a quote through our website to get started.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
